<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Comfortaa:wght@300..700&family=Manrope:wght@200..800&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400;1,600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="container">
        <span>PORTFOLIO © 2024</span>
        <h1 class="index__fullname">Максим<br>Глухов</h1>
        <img class="index-image-heart" src="/images/heart.png" alt="Картинка с сердцем">
        <p class="index__description">Front-end разработчик с 3-летним опытом работы. Еще учусь, но уже кое-что умею.</p>
        <div class="buttons_wrapper">
            <button class="button_projects" onclick="location.href='/projects'">
                <a href="/projects">Посмотреть проекты</a>
            </button>
            <button class="button_contact" onclick="location.href='/contacts'"> 
                <img src="/images/Write.png" alt="Связаться с нами">
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="quotation">
        <img class="quotation_img" src="/images/quotation_mark.svg" alt="Кавычки">
        <div class="quotation_text">Мы довольны сайтом, получилось отлично привлечь клиентов за счет хорошей CEO оптимизации и качественного интерфейса.</div>
        <span class="quotation_signiture">Владимир Егоров, основатель Mixtip</span>
    </div>
    <div class="contacts__wrapper container_without_border">
        <div class="socials">
            <div class="social">
                <a href="https://vk.com/glukhov_gt" target="_blank" class="social_card_wrapper">
                    <img class="social_card_quotation" src="/images/quotation_mark.svg" alt="Кавычки">
                    <div class="social_card_bottom">
                        <img class="social_card_arrow" src="/images/forward.png" alt="Стрелка">
                        <span>Vkontate</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social">
                <a href="https://t.me/maxim_glukhov_abk" target="_blank" class="social_card_wrapper">
                    <img class="social_card_quotation" src="/images/quotation_mark.svg" alt="Кавычки">
                    <div class="social_card_bottom">
                        <img class="social_card_arrow" src="/images/forward.png" alt="Стрелка">
                        <span>Telegram</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social">
                <a href="https://wa.me/79503065151" target="_blank" class="social_card_wrapper">
                    <img class="social_card_quotation" src="/images/quotation_mark.svg" alt="Кавычки">
                    <div class="social_card_bottom">
                        <img class="social_card_arrow" src="/images/forward.png" alt="Стрелка">
                        <span>WhatsApp</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social">
                <a href="mailto:glukhov_maxim@mail.ru" class="social_card_wrapper">
                    <img class="social_card_quotation" src="/images/quotation_mark.svg" alt="Кавычки">
                    <div class="social_card_bottom">
                        <img class="social_card_arrow" src="/images/forward.png" alt="Стрелка">
                        <span>Mail</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact_form">
            <span class="contacts_header">
                Если вам нужна помощь, свяжитесь со мной любым удобным способом.
            </span>
            <span class="contacts_email">
                Email
            </span>
            <a href="mailto:glukhov_maxim@mail.ru" class="contacts_link">
                <img src="/images/forward.png" alt="Стрелка">
                <span class="contacts_link_email">glukhov_maxim@mail.ru</span>
            </a>
            <div class="contact_form_wrapper">
                <p>
                    Введите свои данные
                </p>
                <form class="contact_inputs_wrapper" action="#">
                    <input type="text" class="contact_form_input" placeholder="Имя">
                    <input type="email" class="contact_form_input" placeholder="Почта">
                    <input type="url" class="contact_form_input" placeholder="URL сайта">
                    <input type="text" class="contact_form_input" placeholder="Ваш бюджет">
                    <input type="text" class="contact_form_input" placeholder="Dетали проекта">
                    <button class="contact_form_button">Отправить</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
<script>
    window.addEventListener('scroll', function () {
            const quotation = document.querySelector('.quotation');
            const rect = quotation.getBoundingClientRect(); 

            if (rect.top < window.innerHeight && rect.bottom >= 0) {
                quotation.classList.add('visible'); 
            } else {
                quotation.classList.remove('visible');
            }
        });
</script>

</html>